## Tooling (Terraform)

- `mise install` — terraform + tflint + pre-commit, pinned in `mise.toml`
- `mise run fmt` — `terraform fmt -recursive` · `mise run lint` — tflint
- `mise run validate` — `terraform init -backend=false` + `terraform validate` (offline)
- `mise run plan` — `terraform init` + `terraform plan`
- Pre-commit runs `terraform_fmt` + `terraform_tflint` on commit; tflint config is `.tflint.hcl`.
- State and `*.tfvars` hold secrets — gitignored, never committed. The `.terraform.lock.hcl` lockfile IS committed. Configure the backend per environment.
